+		 * return value of lnet_eq_wait_locked:
+		 * -1 : did nothing and it's sure no new event
+		 *  1 : sleep inside and wait until new event
+		 *  0 : don't want to wait anymore, but might have new event
+		 *      so need to call dequeue again
